	(text "Specification: \nThe Submodule Legs: \n-Bidirectional current: +-2.5A \n-Submodule: 5V 	\n-Max Terminal V Difference +VDC, -VDC = 35V\n-Max Frequency on leg: \n	50Hz\n-Submodules will be switching at max 120KHz\n"
