	(text "The display is driven by ssd1306. \nExisting library for stm32 can be found here: \nhttps://github.com/afiskon/stm32-ssd1306\nhttps://github.com/RobertoBenjami/stm32_ssd1306_i2c_dma_hal\nhttps://github.com/4ilo/ssd1306-stm32HAL"
